{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"13e4f6ce98","title":"给黄炎培的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"4541eb7b97","index":0,"year":1957,"month":2,"day":11,"articleId":"13e4f6ce98"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji37","name":"毛泽东全集第37卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/37-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji37":{"comments":[{"id":"5c76b60daf","publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"13e4f6ce98","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"黄炎培，字任之，当时任中国民主建国会主任委员、全国人大常委会副委员长。"},{"id":"11f3b5e7d3","publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"13e4f6ce98","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这是毛泽东1956年6月写的《水调歌头·游泳》中的一句。毛泽东曾在1956年12月4日将这首词录赠黄炎培。"}],"contents":[{"id":"c46a7d871e","type":"title","text":"给黄炎培的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"13e4f6ce98"},{"id":"5c76b60daf","type":"paragraph","text":"任之先生：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"13e4f6ce98"},{"id":"11f3b5e7d3","type":"paragraph","text":"惠书盛意可感！那些东西，既已发表，不改也可。游长江二小时飘三十多里才达彼岸，可见水流之急。都是仰游侧游，故用“极目楚天舒”为宜。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"13e4f6ce98"},{"id":"80fe2d3855","type":"paragraph","text":"顺致敬意！","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"13e4f6ce98"},{"id":"809d7c7787","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"13e4f6ce98"},{"id":"76beef513d","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五七年二月十一日","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"13e4f6ce98"}],"page":{"id":"231c6343b2","publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"13e4f6ce98","start":274,"end":274}}}},"__N_SSG":true}